  "prompt": "What are some ways to call the US from Italy?",
  "response": "Here are several ways to call the US from Italy:\n\n1. Using a mobile phone\n- Dial +1 (US country code)\n- Then the area code\n- Followed by the phone number\n- Example: +1 (area code) (phone number)\n\n2. Using a landline\n- Dial 00 (international prefix)\n- Then 1 (US country code)\n- Then the area code\n- Followed by the phone number\n- Example: 00 1 (area code) (phone number)\n\n3. VoIP services\n- Skype\n- WhatsApp\n- Zoom\n- Google Voice\n\n4. Calling cards\n- Purchase an international calling card\n- Follow instructions on the card\n- Usually involves dialing a specific access number\n\n5. Mobile apps\n- Viber\n- FaceTime\n- Facebook Messenger\n- WhatsApp video/voice calls\n\n6. Internet-based calling services\n- Google Voice\n- Vonage\n- Magic Jack\n\nTips:\n- Check with your mobile carrier about international calling rates\n- Consider using Wi-Fi for cheaper/free calls\n- Be aware of time zone differences\n- Some services require both parties to have the same app installed",
